This is a sugar for the Erlang language.

Installation:

I. Via plain archive download (gzip/tar/zip).
 1. download the sugar from github
 2. expand the archive
 3. move the erlang.sugar bundle in YOUR_HOME_FOLDER/Library/Application Support/Espresso/Sugars/
 4. restart Espresso

II. Via git.
 1. Make sure you have git installed (either via macports, or direct install, or fink).
 2. Open Terminal.app
 3. Type: "mkdir -p ~/Library/Application Support/Espresso/Sugars". 
 4. Type: "cd ~/Library/Application Support/Espresso/Sugars"
 5. Type: "git clone git://github.com/nickhristov/erlang.sugar.git".
 6. Restart espresso.

 The advantage of this method is that you can very easily get updates by doing.
 7. Type: "cd ~/Library/Application Support/Espresso/Sugars/erlang.sugar"
 8. Type: "git pull master".

